-- Rolls Royce Group Chief Rose to Retire, to Be Replaced by Ahold's Rishton
-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 2010-09-30T06:06:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/rolls-royce-group-chief-rose-to-retire-to-be-replaced-by-ahold-s-rishton.html
Rolls-Royce Group Plc said Chief
Executive Officer John Rose will retire at the end of March next
year, to be succeeded by John Rishton, currently chief
executive of Royal Ahold NV.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Altaner at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net  